Package net.canarymod

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlockIterator
    Iterator wrapper for a LineTracer
    Canary
    The interface to the brains of the bird! AKA Utils
    CanaryClassLoader
    Canary Class Loader

    Used to load and manage plugin jars/classes
    CanaryClassWatcher
    Canary Class Watcher

    Designed to allow plugins to share classes between each other.
    NOTE: If a class isn't loaded, this will load the class from the first ClassLoader that has the class.
    It could be an incorrect class or improperly initialized.
    LineTracer
    Traces the line of sight of an entity.
    MathHelp
    Helper class for math methods
    NativeTranslateBridge
    A Bridge class to adapt the native translation of Minecraft into the Canary Translator.
    ToolBox
    Set of miscellaneous tools
    Translator
    This class handles internationalization (aka i18n).
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CanaryDeserializeException
    Exception that will be thrown if the serialized String of a CanarySerializable object does not have the expected length
